{"id":24,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":24,"title":"Matthew 22","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 22"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus gives the parable of the marriage of the king’s son—Pay tribute to Cæsar and to God—Worldly marriages endure in this life only—The first commandment is to love the Lord—Jesus asks, What think ye of Christ?"]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.1","order":"03.03.022.2815"},["b","1"],"And Jesus answered and spake unto them again by parables, and said,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.2","order":"03.03.022.2816"},["b","2"],"The kingdom of heaven is like unto a certain king, which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"made"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"marriage"],"for his son,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.3","order":"03.03.022.2817"},["b","3"],"And sent forth his servants to call them that were bidden to the wedding: and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"they would not come"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.4","order":"03.03.022.2818"},["b","4"],"Again, he sent forth other servants, saying, Tell them which are bidden, Behold, I have prepared my dinner: my oxen and",["i","my"],"fatlings",["i","are"],"killed, and all things",["i","are"],"ready: come unto the marriage."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.5","order":"03.03.022.2819"},["b","5"],"But they made light of",["i","it,"],"and went their ways, one to his farm, another to his merchandise:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.6","order":"03.03.022.2820"},["b","6"],"And the remnant took his servants, and entreated",["i","them"],"spitefully, and slew",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.7","order":"03.03.022.2821"},["b","7"],"But when the king heard",["i","thereof,"],"he was wroth: and he sent forth his armies, and destroyed those murderers, and burned up their city."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.8","order":"03.03.022.2822"},["b","8"],"Then saith he to his servants, The wedding is ready, but they which were bidden were not worthy."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.9","order":"03.03.022.2823"},["b","9"],"Go ye therefore into the highways, and as many as ye shall find, bid to the marriage."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.10","order":"03.03.022.2824"},["b","10"],"So those servants went out into the highways, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"gathered"],"together all as many as they found, both bad and good: and the wedding was furnished with guests."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.11","order":"03.03.022.2825"},["b","11"],"¶And when the king came in to see the guests, he saw there a man which had not on a wedding",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"garment"],":"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.12","order":"03.03.022.2826"},["b","12"],"And he saith unto him, Friend, how camest thou in hither not having a wedding garment? And he was speechless."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.13","order":"03.03.022.2827"},["b","13"],"Then said the king to the servants, Bind him hand and foot, and take him away, and cast",["i","him"],"into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"outer darkness"],"; there shall be weeping and gnashing of teeth."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.14","order":"03.03.022.2828"},["b","14"],"For many are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"called"],", but few",["i","are"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"chosen"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.15","order":"03.03.022.2829"},["b","15"],"¶Then went the Pharisees, and took counsel how they might",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"entangle"],"him in",["i","his"],"talk."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.16","order":"03.03.022.2830"},["b","16"],"And they sent out unto him their disciples with the Herodians, saying, Master, we know that thou art true, and teachest the way of God in truth,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"neither"],"carest thou for any",["i","man:"],"for thou",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"regardest"],"not the person of men."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.17","order":"03.03.022.2831"},["b","17"],"Tell us therefore, What thinkest thou? Is it",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"lawful"],"to give tribute unto Cæsar, or not?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.18","order":"03.03.022.2832"},["b","18"],"But Jesus perceived their wickedness, and said, Why",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"tempt ye"],"me,",["i","ye"],"hypocrites?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.19","order":"03.03.022.2833"},["b","19"],"Shew me the tribute money. And they brought unto him a penny."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.20","order":"03.03.022.2834"},["b","20"],"And he saith unto them, Whose",["i","is"],"this image and superscription?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.21","order":"03.03.022.2835"},["b","21"],"They say unto him, Cæsar’s. Then saith he unto them,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Render"],"therefore unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Cæsar"],"the things which are Cæsar’s; and unto God the things that are God’s."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.22","order":"03.03.022.2836"},["b","22"],"When they had heard",["i","these words,"],"they marvelled, and left him, and went their way."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.23","order":"03.03.022.2837"},["b","23"],"¶The same day came to him the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Sadducees"],", which say that there is no resurrection, and asked him,"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.24","order":"03.03.022.2838"},["b","24"],"Saying, Master, Moses said, If a man die, having no children, his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"brother"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"marry"],"his wife, and raise up seed unto his brother."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.25","order":"03.03.022.2839"},["b","25"],"Now there were with us seven brethren: and the first, when he had married a wife, deceased, and, having no issue, left his wife unto his brother:"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.26","order":"03.03.022.2840"},["b","26"],"Likewise the second also, and the third, unto the seventh."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.27","order":"03.03.022.2841"},["b","27"],"And last of all the woman died also."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.28","order":"03.03.022.2842"},["b","28"],"Therefore in the resurrection whose wife shall she be of the seven? for they all had her."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.29","order":"03.03.022.2843"},["b","29"],"Jesus answered and said unto them, Ye do err, not knowing the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"scriptures"],", nor the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"power"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.30","order":"03.03.022.2844"},["b","30"],"For in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"resurrection"],"they neither",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"marry"],", nor are given in marriage, but are as the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_30c"},"angels"],"of God in heaven."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.31","order":"03.03.022.2845"},["b","31"],"But as touching the resurrection of the dead, have ye not read that which was spoken unto you by God, saying,"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.32","order":"03.03.022.2846"},["b","32"],"I am the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"God"],"of Abraham, and the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob? God is not the God of the dead, but of the living."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.33","order":"03.03.022.2847"},["b","33"],"And when the multitude heard",["i","this,"],"they were astonished at his doctrine."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.34","order":"03.03.022.2848"},["b","34"],"¶But when the Pharisees had heard that he had put the Sadducees to silence, they were gathered together."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.35","order":"03.03.022.2849"},["b","35"],"Then one of them,",["i","which was"],"a lawyer, asked",["i","him a question,"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"tempting"],"him, and saying,"],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.36","order":"03.03.022.2850"},["b","36"],"Master, which",["i","is"],"the great commandment in the law?"],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.37","order":"03.03.022.2851"},["b","37"],"Jesus said unto him, Thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"love"],"the Lord thy God with all thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"heart"],", and with all thy soul, and with all thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_37c"},"mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.38","order":"03.03.022.2852"},["b","38"],"This is the first and great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"commandment"],"."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.39","order":"03.03.022.2853"},["b","39"],"And the second",["i","is"],"like unto it, Thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"love"],"thy neighbour as thyself."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.40","order":"03.03.022.2854"},["b","40"],"On these two commandments hang all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"law"],"and the prophets."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.41","order":"03.03.022.2855"},["b","41"],"¶While the Pharisees were gathered together, Jesus asked them,"],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.42","order":"03.03.022.2856"},["b","42"],"Saying, What think ye of Christ? whose son is he? They say unto him,",["i","The Son"],"of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"David"],"."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.43","order":"03.03.022.2857"},["b","43"],"He saith unto them, How then doth David in spirit call him Lord, saying,"],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.44","order":"03.03.022.2858"},["b","44"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto my Lord, Sit thou on my right hand, till I make thine enemies thy footstool?"],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.45","order":"03.03.022.2859"},["b","45"],"If David then call him Lord, how is he his son?"],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.46","order":"03.03.022.2860"},["b","46"],"And no man was able to answer him a word, neither",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_46a"},"durst"],"any",["i","man"],"from that day forth ask him any more",["i","questions."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.2a","order":"03.03.022.2861"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"gave a wedding celebration."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.2b","order":"03.03.022.2863"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/5.34"},"Luke 5:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.7.7-9"},"Rev. 19:7 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/21.2"},"21:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.3"},"D&C 65:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.3a","order":"03.03.022.2865"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"they did not want to come."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.10a","order":"03.03.022.2867"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.47.47-53"},"Matt. 13:47 (47–53)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.11a","order":"03.03.022.2869"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.8"},"Rev. 19:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.13a","order":"03.03.022.2871"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12.11-12"},"Matt. 8:12 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.8"},"D&C 77:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.72.71-73"},"133:72 (71–73)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.14a","order":"03.03.022.2873"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.34.34-40"},"D&C 121:34 (34–40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.14b","order":"03.03.022.2875"},["b","14b"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 22:14 … chosen;",["i","wherefore all do not have on the wedding garment."]],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.15a","order":"03.03.022.2877"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.13.13-17"},"Mark 12:13 (13–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/11.54"},"Luke 11:54"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.20.19-26"},"20:20 (19–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.16a","order":"03.03.022.2879"},["b","16a"],["span.small","IE"],"you court no man’s favor."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.16b","order":"03.03.022.2881"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/24.23"},"Prov. 24:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.17a","order":"03.03.022.2883"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.22.20-23"},"D&C 58:22 (20–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.18a","order":"03.03.022.2885"},["b","18a"],["span.small","GR"],"are you testing.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.21a","order":"03.03.022.2887"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.21b","order":"03.03.022.2889"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/governments"},"TG Governments"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.23a","order":"03.03.022.2891"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.12.1,6,11-12"},"Matt. 16:12 (1, 6, 11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.8"},"Acts 23:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.24a","order":"03.03.022.2893"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/25.5"},"Deut. 25:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.19"},"Mark 12:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.24b","order":"03.03.022.2895"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ruth/3.13"},"Ruth 3:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.29a","order":"03.03.022.2897"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.1.1-4"},"D&C 138:1 (1–4)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-teaching-mode-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Teaching Mode of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-study-of"},"Scriptures, Study of"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.29b","order":"03.03.022.2899"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.30a","order":"03.03.022.2901"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"30b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.30b","order":"03.03.022.2903"},["b","30b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-marry"},"TG Marriage, Marry"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-temporal"},"Marriage, Temporal"],"."],["div",{"id":"30c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.30c","order":"03.03.022.2905"},["b","30c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/131.4.1-4"},"D&C 131:4 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.16.15-17"},"132:16 (15–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.32a","order":"03.03.022.2907"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/32.9"},"Gen. 32:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.10"},"1 Ne. 19:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.21"},"D&C 136:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.35a","order":"03.03.022.2909"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.37a","order":"03.03.022.2911"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dedication"},"TG Dedication"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"God, Love of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"37b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.37b","order":"03.03.022.2913"},["b","37b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heart"},"TG Heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"37c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.37c","order":"03.03.022.2915"},["b","37c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.38a","order":"03.03.022.2917"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commandments-of-god"},"TG Commandments of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"39a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.39a","order":"03.03.022.2919"},["b","39a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.40a","order":"03.03.022.2921"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.33.13-37"},"Mark 12:33 (13–37)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/13.10.8-10"},"Rom. 13:10 (8–10)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"42a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.42a","order":"03.03.022.2923"},["b","42a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-davidic-descent-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Davidic Descent of"],"."],["div",{"id":"46a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.46a","order":"03.03.022.2925"},["b","46a"],["span.small","GR"],"dared."]]}
